neuragenix.dao
Class DBSchema

java.lang.Object
  neuragenix.dao.DBSchema
public class DBSchema
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains all the Database schema settings for the platformgenix. It is used to: 1. Hold all the table names (as domains), links between tables, internal and database field names, field types, serial keys for the tables, which fields are required fields.
2. Hold static variables used by the dao and channels to use the dao
3. Hold database connectors and operators for the dao

It will throw an exception if the number of field names do not match the number of field types. So if you add a field name you must add it's type!
